{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Stripe Sync Engine","version":"1.0.0","description":"Stripe Sync Engine — stateless, one-shot source/destination sync over HTTP.\nAll sync endpoints accept configuration via the `X-Pipeline` header (JSON-encoded PipelineConfig). Optional cursor state can be provided via `X-State`.\n\n## Endpoints\n\n| Method | Path | Summary |\n|--------|------|---------|\n| GET | /health | Health check |\n| POST | /setup | Set up destination schema |\n| POST | /teardown | Tear down destination schema |\n| GET | /check | Check connector connection |\n| POST | /discover | Discover available streams |\n| POST | /read | Read records from source |\n| POST | /write | Write records to destination |\n| POST | /sync | Run sync pipeline (read → write) |\n| GET | /meta/sources | List available source connectors |\n| GET | /meta/sources/:type | Get source connector spec |\n| GET | /meta/destinations | List available destination connectors |\n| GET | /meta/destinations/:type | Get destination connector spec |"},"paths":{"/health":{"get":{"operationId":"health","tags":["Status"],"summary":"Health check","responses":{"200":{"description":"Server is healthy","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"object","properties":{"ok":{"type":"boolean","const":true}},"required":["ok"],"additionalProperties":false}}}}}}},"/setup":{"post":{"operationId":"pipeline_setup","tags":["Stateless Sync API"],"summary":"Set up destination schema","description":"Creates destination tables and applies migrations. Safe to call multiple times.","parameters":[{"in":"header","name":"x-pipeline","description":"JSON-encoded PipelineConfig: { source: { type, ...config }, destination: { type, ...config }, streams }","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/PipelineConfig"}}}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Setup complete","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"object","propertyNames":{"type":"string"},"additionalProperties":{}}}}},"400":{"des